import React from 'react';
import {CDBFooter, CDBBox, CDBIcon, CDBBtn, CDBFooterLink, CDBContainer} from 'cdbreact';

export const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <CDBFooter className="shadow">
      <CDBBox display="flex" flex="column" className="mx-auto py-5 " style={{ width: '90%' }}>
        <CDBBox display="flex" justifyContent="between" className="flex-wrap">
          <CDBBox alignSelf="center">
            
            <CDBBox className="mt-5 cont" display="flex">
              <CDBBtn flat color="dark" className="p-2">
                <CDBIcon fab icon="facebook-f" />
              </CDBBtn>
              <CDBBtn flat color="dark" className="mx-3 p-2">
                <CDBIcon fab icon="twitter" />
              </CDBBtn>
              <CDBBtn flat color="dark" className="p-2">
                <CDBIcon fab icon="instagram" />
              </CDBBtn>
            </CDBBox>
          </CDBBox>

          <CDBBox>
            <CDBBox display="flex" flex="column" style={{ cursor: 'pointer' }}>
              <CDBFooterLink href="/">Home</CDBFooterLink>
            </CDBBox>
          </CDBBox>

          <CDBBox>
            <CDBBox display="flex" flex="column" style={{ cursor: 'pointer' }}>
              <CDBFooterLink href="/">Kontakt</CDBFooterLink>
            </CDBBox>
          </CDBBox>

          <CDBBox>
            <CDBBox display="flex" flex="column" style={{ cursor: 'pointer' }}>
              <CDBFooterLink href="/">Support</CDBFooterLink>
            </CDBBox>
          </CDBBox>

        </CDBBox>
        <small className="text-center mt-5">© Devwares, 2022. All rights reserved.</small>
      </CDBBox>
    </CDBFooter>
  );
};
